snippet.title: G for Gaming
snippet.description:
hey friends :) 
welcome to our GAMiNG CHANNEL!!

i'm Adley if you didn't know.. i make fun videos with my family on my main youtube called A for Adley!

my mom and dad both loved to play video games while they were growing up.. and now our WHOLE FAMiLY loves to play them together! i have a little brother named Niko that LOVES to play Minecraft and Roblox with me, i also have a little sister, Navey,  who is a little to young to play games now.. but she loves to watch us play!

AND.. i have some games of my own called "Adley's PlaySpace" and "Unicorn Catch"!! you can play them from the app store, google play, the amazon app store, or on my website AforAdley.com  :) oh and i almost forgot the best part.. they are TOTALLY free with NO ads!! 

Thanks for Watching!
